_sText:
It is a remake of my map "ze_Get_To_The_Chopper".

main rule: 
HUMANS NEED TO PRESS EACH BUTTON IN 30 SECONDS!

Cannon control:
W - raise up
S - lower down
A - turn left
D - turn right
left mouse button - fire

Humans, be careful!

***WORKS ON ORANGE BOX ENGINE!!!***
***people do not fall through a helicopter. (starting with b13)***
